These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
3 different pets are kept: ferret, rabbit, hedgehog
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, january, august
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: aconite, sunflower, marigold
There are 3 different favourite colors: pink, white, black
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, epic, satire
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, german, italian
3 different games are played: bridge, monopoly, go
 1. the person playing bridge is the german##1
 2. the person playing go is the person who likes black##1
 3. the owner of the hedgehog is between the italian and the owner of the rabbit##2
 4. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the colombian##1
 5. the person who likes white is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 6. the person who growsmarigold is the colombian##1
 7. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 8. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 9. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person who likes white##1
10. the person who growssunflower is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Pet      | rabbit    | hedgehog   | ferret           |
| Birthday          | january       | august    | december         |
| Flower         | sunflower    | marigold  | aconite        |
| Color           | pink | white   | black      |
| Movie-Genre   | epic        | satire    | disaster       |
| Nationality   | german     | colombian  | italian       |
| Game         | bridge     | monopoly | go |

