.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-2::.
City: berlin, hannover, new-york
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, subway, trike
There are 3 different favourite colors: turquise, brown, pink
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, amaryllis, iris
