3 different pets are kept: dog, horse, pony
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, police-officer, lawyer
 1. the owner of the pony is the futuristic house##1
 2. the owner of the pony is the person who likes pink##1
 3. the person who likes pink is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 4. the accountant is between the person traveling to hannover and the person traveling to berlin##2
 5. the modern house is on the far left##1
 6. the person traveling to hannover is the person who growsdaffodil##1
 7. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the lawyer##1
 8. the person driving the taxi is the person who likes turquise##1
 9. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
10. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| City      | berlin   | new-york    | hannover         |
| Transport          | taxi    | subway | trike          |
| Color   | turquise  | pink  | brown     |
| Flower   | iris       | amaryllis      | daffodil         |
| House   | modern      | futuristic   | farmhouse    |
| Pet           | dog        | pony      | horse         |
| Job         | police-officer | accountant  | lawyer |

