 3. the person watching adventure movies is the person driving the ship##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is the person traveling to miami##1
 5. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 6. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 7. the writer is between the person drinking almond-milk and the tower house##2
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the futuristic house##1
 9. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
10. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person driving the train##1
11. the person drinking almond-milk is the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
