 4. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 5. the person driving the van is between the person traveling to miami and the person eating peach##2
 6. the person eating corn is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
 7. the person driving the van is the aristoff-smoker##1
 8. the musician is the person playing go##1
 9. the person eating corn is between the musician and the social-worker##2
10. the tower house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1

.:: Answer ::.
