The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, chef, electrician
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, blend, davidoff
There are 3 different favourite colors: lilac, ebony, black
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, soccer, water-polo
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: techno, country, punk
 1. the person who's sport is water-polo is in the middle##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in april is in the middle##1
 3. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 4. the person traveling to rome is the chef##1
 5. the fan of techno is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
 6. the person who likes black is on the left of the chef##1
 7. the fan of punk is between the person who's birthday is in january and the fonseca-smoker##2
 8. the journalist is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 9. the chef is the fan of techno##1
10. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
11. the fan of techno is the fonseca-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Birthday      | january | april      | march      |
| City         | marseilles     | miami     | rome  |
| Job   | electrician | journalist  | chef |
| Cigar   | blend  | davidoff     | fonseca |
| Color           | lilac        | black | ebony     |
| Sport         | handball    | water-polo | soccer   |
| Music-Genre     | country        | punk        | techno   |

