.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, vegafina, bongani
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, mango, pumpkin
City: liverpool, prague, edinburgh
House: cottage, cape-cod, victorian
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, march, december
There are 3 different favourite colors: coral, red, fuchsia
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, orchid, daisy
1. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the victorian house##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
3. the person eating mango is on the left of the cottage house##1
4. the person who likes coral is between the person who's birthday is in september and the cape-cod house##2
5. the person eating pumpkin is between the victorian house and the person traveling to edinburgh##2
6. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
7. the person who likes red is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
8. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
9. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
