4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person playing domino##1
5. the dancer is between the owner of the rabbit and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
6. the journalist is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
7. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
8. the person playing backgammon is the person who's birthday is in january##1
9. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1

