.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: mauve, turquise, black
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, rock-climbing, traveling
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: punk, d&b, soul
City: new-york, colone, edinburgh
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, begonia, daisy
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, zombie, comedy
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, roller
1. the person who likes mauve is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person driving the roller is the person watching epic movies##1
3. the fan of punk is between the person who likes black and the person who growsdaisy##2
4. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
7. the fan of d&b is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
8. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
9. the person traveling to colone is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Color      | turquise    | mauve       | black      |
| Hobby          | filmmaking   | traveling   | rock-climbing  |
| Music-Genre           | d&b  | punk | soul    |
| City   | new-york   | colone     | edinburgh  |
| Flower           | daisy     | balloon-flower        | begonia |
| Movie-Genre         | zombie | epic   | comedy  |
| Transport     | jet-ski    | roller     | car      |

 